cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.DS 

The paper proposes the use of machine learning for the fusion of multiple statistical algorithms to improve outbreak detection. This involves the use of p-values and additional features for training a fusion classifier. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the following sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks)
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms)
